In a small bowl, add @cane vinegar{1/2%cup} , @water{2%tbsp} , @fish sauce{1%tsp} , @brown sugar{2%tsp} ,  @finely chopped shallot{1} , @finely chopped garlic{} , @salt ,  and @black pepper{} (to taste)

Whisk until sugar is dissolved.

Let it stand for ~{30%minutes} .

Do a taste test before serving and adjust sugar, water, salt, and black pepper, to taste. 

The water will help lessen the sourness. Omit if preferred.